  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catalyst: From the stars, a Souls-Like First person shooter. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game features High octane Parry based combat and thrilling multi-phase boss fights with a boss rush style of progression broken up by levels with rich collectable lore tablets. Maybe if you find them all, you can unlock the secrets of the Catalyst...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511330/extras/a9beb0e04326fe189f2d77f4ed1f7231.avif?t=1740657553\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511330/extras_big/a9beb0e04326fe189f2d77f4ed1f7231.avif?t=1740657553 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple BossFights, Endless mode, And 4 Difficulties to choose Its up to you how to play CATALYST.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511330/extras/c60b8c3f9fefbc8fd3a084286c5167de.avif?t=1740657553\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511330/extras_big/c60b8c3f9fefbc8fd3a084286c5167de.avif?t=1740657553 width=800 height=800 /></span></p>",
